      "writtenOn": "2021-07-09T12:24:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The `go vet` static analyzer throws warnings about this, for good reason. It results in copying a mutex that is internal to the server struct (a sync.Once).\n\nYou\u0027ll want to pass it in as a pointer.",
