      "writtenOn": "2021-07-09T12:24:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "suggestion: Add a context.Context [1] as the first param to this function and add it to this request via WithContext [2]. This allows us to more easily inject test-related things. For example, we have this nice now package [3] which allows us to fake the time using contexts. I\u0027ve also used it for faking login status. It might be overkill for now, so it\u0027s fine to omit.\n\n[1] https://blog.golang.org/context#TOC_3.2.\n[2] https://golang.org/pkg/net/http/#Request.WithContext\n[3] https://github.com/google/skia-buildbot/blob/9b3f4fb533b9ab914c6730dc664d9caf59e36c01/go/now/now.go#L15",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 47,
        "startChar": 1,
        "endLine": 47,
        "endChar": 2
      },
      "revId": "0b1ac519f8689683aa9dd457c9aca50f2777426c",
